   Syntax     : PICKFILE( [FILESPEC] )

   Parameters : FILESPEC is a DOS filename. Wildcards permitted

   Returns    : Character file name of selected file or "" if nothing picked.

   Example    : yourfile := pickfile( '*.dbf' )

